{
  "stem": "1169.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is something you learn here in the third grade, fourth grade, fifth grade.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Were you asked about your experiences, what you went through, once you came to school here?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That really was mind boggling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] I was amazed no one asked me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I just came from there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No one, so-called debriefed me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not the kids, not the teachers, not the principals-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] nobody, absolutely nobody.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] People looked at us as a refugee family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We moved into East Flatbush.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I must tell you, they were unusually nice to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We moved into a neighborhood that was not religious.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, again, this tradition that we started in Bergen-Belsen of working primarily with a-religious people just, by chance, continued here.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We got on very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And everybody had-- like, had pity on us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But no one asked us, tell your story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was not until [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 25 years later-- probably more, 28 years later-- until about '73, '74 that I was asked to speak about the Shoah, about the Holocaust, and went around to various schools, and synagogues, and temples.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't know if I will ever understand this phenomenon that this was a taboo subject in the American Jew society.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Until about 1970, no one discussed the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I'm very pleased that today it's on the forefront, it's on the front lines.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And large cities are competing with each other in building Holocaust memorials and museums.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it's becoming part and parcel of curriculums.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there's an awareness.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I-- I-- I have no way to understand why, in the first 25 years after the Holocaust, nobody cared about it.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
